Package io.github.neonorbit.dexplore.reference

References to constants that resides in the constant pool.

These are basically strings, classes, methods and fields used in the source code.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

Reference Types:

  • StringReference: reference to a string literal
  • TypeReference: reference to a constant containing full name of a class
  • FieldReference: reference to a constant containing a field details
  • MethodReference: reference to a constant containing a method details
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DexRefData  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FieldRefData
    This class represents a reference to a field.
    MethodRefData
    This class represents a reference to a method.
    StringRefData
    This class represents a reference to a literal string.
    TypeRefData
    This class represents a reference to a type (eg: the full name of a class).
